verses.verse: Neither let those who pass by them say, (Ps. 37:2) “The blessing of the LORD be upon you; We bless you in the name of the LORD!”
Waiting for the Redemption of the LORD A Song of Ascents. [1] Out (Ruth 2:4) of the depths I have cried to You, O LORD;
Lord, hear my voice! Let Your ears be attentive To the voice of my supplications.
